SLS 26RS-661 ORIGINAL
2026 Regular Session
SENATE CONCURRENT RESOLUTION NO. 1
BY SENATOR BARROW
LEGISLATIVE SESSIONS. Invites the governor to address a joint session of the legislature
on Monday, March 9, 2026, at 1 p.m.
1 A CONCURRENT RESOLUTION
2 To invite the Honorable Jeff Landry, Governor of Louisiana, to address a joint session of the
3 legislature.
4 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
5 invite the Honorable Jeff Landry, Governor of Louisiana, to address the House of
6 Representatives and the Senate in a joint session to be convened on Monday, March 9, 2026,
7 at 1 p.m.
8 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that for this purpose, the House of Representatives
9 and the Senate shall meet in a joint session in the chamber of the House of Representatives.
